706813f-a.title: Brooklyn: Smith Street - Huntington Street
706813f-a.text:
Smith Street, west side, south of Huntington Street. West
9th Street is seen in the foreground with the gasoline truck thereon.
June 9, 1938.
P. L. Sperr
NO REPRODUCTIONS.

706814f-a.title: Brooklyn: Smith Street - Huntington Street
706814f-a.text:
Smith Street, east side, south from Huntington to West 9th Streets,
showing Eighth Ave., Subway line overhead.
June S, 1932.
P. L. Sperr.
